{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But there was a lot of dollars were falsified.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Until one day, through a friend of a friend, I was told that somebody in the bank, in an official German bank, was selling dollars for zlotys, on the black market again.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I really purchased dollars from him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And those dollars, I managed to smuggle all the way through Slovakia and Hungary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I finally came to Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the dollars were in the heel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Some of them were still in the heel of my boots.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I took them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I went to Barclays Bank, which is a big British bank.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was a problem that the money was so-- so squeezed tight, by the time we opened it, it had a lot of holes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But it was genuine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they paid me based on the remaining area of the money like, 78% of the area was still preserved.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They paid me in full for that money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's just to show that under the German eyes, there is somebody in the bank was running his own business selling dollars.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was not unusual.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It sounds unusual today.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the whole economy, everything was black market, total black market.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So how long were you in Warsaw?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Warsaw nine months from-- from September 1942 till July of 1943, which is about for 11 months.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I spent my time--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had this business, which in other words, every two weeks I would go for this type of a shipment, or every three weeks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes maybe every month.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was a number of these shipments, each one very profitable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Other than that, I spent my time roaming through the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
